Screen = home
Design file = design/home_design.json
Spec file   = specs/home_specification.md

Apply:
- prompts/FLUTTER_STANDARDS.md
- prompts/PROJECT_ORGANIZATION.md
- prompts/UI_DSL_MAPPING.md
- prompts/ACCEPTANCE_CRITERIA.md
- prompts/TESTING_STANDARDS.md
- prompts/ARCHITECTURE_GUIDE.md
- prompts/TEMPLATE_BUILD_STATIC_SCREEN.prompt

Generate static code only. Output:
- lib/screens/home_screen.dart
- test/home_screen_test.dart
- plus any reusable components under lib/components/** if patterns are detected.
